{"type":null,"faqId":33120,"title":"如何开启GPS定位？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.108333334in;margin-bottom:0.108333334in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:0pt;border::thin solid black;color:black;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>打开下拉通知栏，点击 GPS 的快捷开关，可快速打开或关闭 GPS 卫星定位。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果想导航定位更精确或更省电，可进入手机设置界面，点击定位服务或位置信息访问权限，根据需要选择不同的定位方法，如使用 WLAN、移动网络或 AGPS 等。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=103543\" style=\"width:2.1909723in;height:3.8972223in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span class=\"s1\">    </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=103544\" style=\"width:2.1972222in;height:3.9069445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=103545\" style=\"width:2.1909723in;height:3.8972223in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":142,"faqType":"位置服务与导航","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7822","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Location-Navigation","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748503000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":21,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":n